# Screenshots Directory

Place your application screenshots here with the following naming convention:

## Required Screenshots:

1. landing.png - Landing/Welcome page
2. login.png - Login screen
3. register.png - Registration screen
4. forgot-password.png - Forgot password screen
5. verify-code.png - SMS verification screen
6. patient-dashboard.png - Patient main dashboard
7. patient-medications.png - Patient medication list
8. patient-profile.png - Patient profile screen
9. confirm-medication.png - Medication confirmation modal
10. doctor-dashboard.png - Doctor dashboard
11. doctor-dashboard-full.png - Doctor dashboard with patient list
12. tutor-dashboard.png - Tutor/Caregiver dashboard
13. patient-profile-doctor.png - Patient profile (as seen by doctor)
14. add-patient.png - Add patient form
15. add-prescription.png - Add prescription form
16. alerts.png - Medication alerts view
17. alarm-activity.png - Full-screen alarm (from device)
18. voice-recorder.png - Voice message recorder
19. offline-mode.png - Offline mode indicator

## Screenshot Guidelines:

- Resolution: 1080x1920 (or device native)
- Format: PNG preferred
- Include device frame if possible
- Capture in both light and dark themes if applicable

